---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from "../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro";
import SubNav from "../../../components/SubNav.astro";
import PageTitle from "../../../components/PageTitle.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import featureImage from '../../../images/featured-images/about-facilities.jpg';
import { YouTube } from 'astro-embed';
import mairGraphic from '../../../images/facilities/m-air-graphic.png';
import mairNight from '../../../images/facilities/m-air-night.jpg';
import mairCamera from '../../../images/facilities/m-air-camera.jpg';
import mairFall from '../../../images/facilities/m-air-fall.jpg';
import ogImage from '/public/social/m-air-night.jpg';
---
<Layout title="M-Air" image={ogImage.src} description="M-Air is a 10,000 sq ft, four-story, netted scientific facility that enables the study of autonomy and collaborative robotics." >
    <Breadcrumbs />
    <PageTitle title="M-Air" image={featureImage} imageAlt="M-Air facility" />
    <article class="prose max-w-6xl w-11/12 mx-auto dark:prose-invert mt-8">
            <div class="mb-8 w-full aspect-video [&>lite-youtube]:!max-w-none">
                <YouTube id="kboyDG_wZSc" posterQuality="max" class="w-full h-full" />
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <p class="mb-4">M-Air is a 10,000 sq ft, four-story, netted scientific facility that enables the study of autonomy and collaborative robotics in the "wild", with emphasis on dealing with the full range of Michigan weather, -30C to 38C, with rain, sleet, wind, and snow.</p>

                    <p class="mb-4">This space enables the evaluation of prototype hardware and algorithms in a safe manner, thereby encouraging risk-taking for rapid exploration of ideas. M-Air accelerates the pursuit of aggressive educational and research flight projects that involve high risk of fly-away or loss-of-controlâ€”and in realistic wind, lighting and sensor conditions. It allows researchers to better understand operational risks associated with real-world outdoor flights with no real risk to people or other aircraft outside the net.</p>

                    <p class="mb-4">M-Air is located on UM's College of Engineering, directly across the street from the Aerospace Department, University of Michigan Wind Tunnels, and the recently completed Robotics Building.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <figure class="mb-4">
                        <Image 
                            src={mairGraphic}
                            alt="M-Air facility diagram"
                            class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-lg"
                            width={1422}
                            height={823}
                        />
                        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Credit: Cosme Ochoa</figcaption>
                    </figure>

                    <p class="mb-4">M-Air infrastructure includes an adjacent covered pavilion for UAV staging, command and control, and data collection, and is equipped with power and tied into UM's data infrastructure. M-Air is equipped with a dense array of all-weather, high resolution motion capture cameras.</p>

                    <p class="mb-4">M-Air is used by our research groups, student teams, and in our robotics courses, and allows Michigan to quickly move ideas from laptop and lab bench to first flight.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8 w-full aspect-video [&>lite-youtube]:!max-w-none">
                <YouTube id="e-x9HHRV6TM" title="M-Air 360 in Summer" posterQuality="max" class="w-full h-full" />
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
                <figure>
                    <Image 
                        src={mairNight}
                        alt="Quadcopter flying at night"
                        class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-lg"
                        width={2048}
                        height={1365}
                    />
                    <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Quadcopter flying at night</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <figure>
                    <Image 
                        src={mairCamera}
                        alt="One of 30 motion capture cameras"
                        class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-lg"
                        width={2048}
                        height={1365}
                    />
                    <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">One of 30 motion capture cameras</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <figure>
                    <Image 
                        src={mairFall}
                        alt="Early fall at M-Air"
                        class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-lg"
                        width={2048}
                        height={1365}
                    />
                    <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Early fall at M-Air</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-umichblue dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">M-Air Calendar</h2>
                    <iframe src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?showPrint=0&showTabs=0&src=umich.edu_q4p3pqpesecd8tlmlcu5aioplg%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=America%2FNew_York" style="border: 0" class="w-full h-[400px]" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-umichblue dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">M-Air contacts</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">To receive announcements and updates about M-Air, join the <a href="https://mcommunity.umich.edu/#group:mair-announce">mair-announce list</a> on MCommunity.</p>

                    <p class="mb-4">For questions or to reserve the facility please contact <a href="mailto:mair-info@umich.edu">mair-info@umich.edu</a>.</p>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-umichblue dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">Schematics</h2>
                    <p>For architectural details, download the <a href="/pdf/m-air-schematics.pdf">construction schematics</a> for M-Air.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</Layout>
